| TEXAS INSTRUMENTS INCORPORATED
| Standard Linear and Logic Group
| IBIS Model of SN74LVC1G126
| SINGLE BUS BUFFER GATE WITH 3-STATE OUTPUT
| This file contains package information for the following:
|  SOT 5-pin (DBV) package as [Component] LVC1G126_DBV
|  SOT 5-pin (DCK) package as [Component] LVC1G126_DCK
|  DSBGA 5-pin (YEA_YZA) package as [Component] LVC1G126_YEA_YZA
|  NanoStar WCSP 5-pin (YEP) package as [Component] LVC1G126_YEP
|  NanoFree WCSP 5-pin (YZP) package as [Component] LVC1G126_YZP
| This device can be powered at the following Vccs:
|  1.8 volt Vcc
|  2.5 volt Vcc
|  3.3 volt Vcc
|  5 volt Vcc
| This file provides unique models under the [Model Selector] for each Vcc.
| For operation at a specific Vcc, select the appropriate model after each
| [Model Selector] keyword.
